.2（临时）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙 VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/tokyo-district-court-rules-the-sale-of-malicious-video-impersonates-a-vtuber-inside-person-performer-and-voice-model-infringes-on-the-rights/">认定伪装成VTuber“内部人士（表演者/配音模特）”的恶意视频销售“侵权”的判决书东京地方法院首次</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; https://p2y.jp/tokyo-district-court-rules-the-sale-of-malicious-video-impersonates-a-vtuber-inside-person-performer-and-voice-model-infringes-on-the-权利/饲料/ 0 93866
